{"type":"message","id":"fe772321","parentId":"4b190800","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:16:50.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying hi to me. This is a direct message from a Feishu user. Looking at the context, I see BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means this is a fresh workspace and I need to follow the bootstrap process to figure out who I am and who they are.\n\nLet me follow BOOTSTRAP.md - I should start a conversation to figure out my name, nature, vibe, and emoji. I should also update IDENTITY.md and USER.md with what I learn.\n\nLet me respond naturally and start the bootstrap conversation.","thinkingSignature":"dae2b48ff674b4b8f161a736a97f38b69d92bceeb9bf68a85bb3dc0b02fc7baf"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just came online in this fresh workspace. Who am I? Who are you? \n\nLet's figure out together what to call me, what kind of creature I am, and how we should work together. What should I know about you?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":166,"cacheRead":10606,"cacheWrite":7720,"totalTokens":18639,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778419003745,"responseId":"064fb83ce7722936e6c530de2b5924c9"}}
