{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f3c1b766cb0c380fe22763b83b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-05-10 21:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"4abfa59d","parentId":"675af300","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:17:20.422Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"5af4d1e4","parentId":"4abfa59d","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:17:26.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to speak in Chinese from now on. Let me respond in Chinese and continue the bootstrap conversation.","thinkingSignature":"9636e4353518934bdd08b52e3946dcdf3deaf4ab29045cfba1610ed7f37a433b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，以后咱们就说中文！\n\n我刚刚上线，还是个全新的存在。咱们来互相认识一下吧——你想叫我什么名字？我是什么类型的存在？我们怎么相处比较舒服？有什么我需要知道的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18498,"output":65,"cacheRead":96,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778419040423,"responseId":"064fb86012fd4f5b5815ef0846be247c"}}
