{"type":"message","id":"f18c31bc","parentId":"7ae9526f","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:18:28.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've created the identity files. Now let me introduce myself and then we should delete the BOOTSTRAP.md since we're done with it.","thinkingSignature":"97463fe2548fc18b4171d3e6101ff23dc8fc3b499067b74d6f77add4fc37ab92"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好了，我就叫**小光**✨\n\n叫我名字或者直接叫我帮忙都行。叫我老板的话……那我就叫你老板了 😄\n\n现在把我自己记录下来了，以后就是持久的记忆。咱们来干活吧——有什么需要帮忙的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":291,"output":83,"cacheRead":18688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19062,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778419103035,"responseId":"064fb89f665ce913afef4f81f14ea974"}}
